Andy Murray blames poor serve and return against Roger Federer
Please turn on JavaScript. Media requires JavaScript to play. Advertisement
Britain's Andy Murray says he served and returned "poorly" during his 6-4 6-2 defeat by Roger Federer at the ATP World Tour Finals and hopes he can pick himself up to qualify for the semi-finals.
